	<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #0064c8;">Croatia â€“ Aveto</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #4a4a4a;"> is web portal designed for owners of tourist facilities (apartments, hotels, camps, tourist agencies) who want to advertise apartments and camps on the Internet.</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #4a4a4a;">If you own a tourist facility and would like to place an ad, you should first register on the site Croatia-Aveto.com.hr. To do that, click on the above link<span style="color: #0064c8;"><a href="registracija" target="_blank"><span style="color: #0064c8;"><em> User Registration</em></span></a>.</span></span></p><br /><br /><p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #0064c8;">REGISTRATION</span></p><br /><ol type="disc"><li>Fields marked with a star are required to enter.</li><li>Data that is not required to enter can be added later.</li><li>After you have enter the data, press the end of white field above the gray padlock. That is a slider and it is set for safety when registering.</li><li>Press the button  <em>Register</em></li><li>When registering you agree to the terms of use of our site that you can read<strong><span style="color: #0064c8;"><a href="uvjeti-oglasavanja-hr" target="_blank"><span style="color: #0064c8;"> HERE</span></a></span></strong></li><li>Remember your username and password that you chosen because you will use them later to login again on site Croatia-Aveto.com.hr.</li></ol><br /><p><br><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #0064c8;">ADDING NEW AD</span></p><br /><ol type="disc"><li>After registration you can enter the ad for your tourist facility.</li><li>Fields framed by red lines are required to enter.</li><li>Data that is not required to enter can be added later, but still provide as much information as you can to make your ad more informative for ad readers.</li><li>For each field, you can read additional description if you put your mouse cursor over its name.</li><li>Once you have completed your ad, you can publish it by clicikng the <em><strong>Save Entry</strong></em> button.</li></ol><br /><p><br><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #0064c8;">PROFILE EDITING</span></p><br /><ol type="disc"><li>Later you can edit your profile and ads that you have already published.</li><li>You can also add new ads.</li><li>It is necessary that every time you want it, you log in with your username and password via<em><strong> Login | Logout .</strong></em></li><li>Login | Logout you can find on the right side of the site.</li><li>After login, you will have access to your user menu, also on the right side of site.</li><li>There you will find all necessary links for editing your data<em> (User profile, Add entry)</em>.</li></ol><br /><p><br><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #0064c8;">FORGOTTEN USERNAME OR PASSWORD</span></p><br /><ol type="disc"><li>Forgotten username or password you can reset via the links on the right side of site:  <em><strong>Forgot your password?</strong></em> and <em><strong>Forgot your username?</strong></em></li><li>Enter the e-mail with which you registered.</li><li>Press the end of white field above the gray padlock. That is a slider and it is set for safety when reseting username and password.</li><li>Press button<em><strong> Submit</strong></em> and send the request to reset the username or password.</li></ol><br /><p><br><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: medium; color: #0064c8;">CONTACT US</span><br><br><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #4a4a4a;">If you will have any question regarding the use of our web pages, please contact us on telephone number +385 01 / 888 77 00 or e-mail address <span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #0064c8;"> info@croatia-aveto.com.hr.</span> <br /></span></p><p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #4a4a4a;"><br /><br /><br />Your Croatia - Aveto team</span></p>
